OL,3,CEdinburgh area locked down after
OL,4,Creports of man with weapons and
OL,5,Cstabbings
OL,7,FPolice have warned the public to avoid
OL,8,Fparts of Edinburgh following "reports
OL,9,Fof a man with a bladed weapon".
OL,11,FLocals say several people may have
OL,12,Fbeen stabbed, with an emergency
OL,13,Fresponse in place since before 9am.
OL,15,FArmed police are at the incident in
OL,16,FCalder in the west of the city.
OL,18,FA statement from Police Scotland said:
OL,19,F"The public is being advised to avoid
OL,20,Fthe Calder area of Edinburgh following
OL,21,Freports of a man with a bladed weapon.
