OL,3,CEdinburgh area locked down after
OL,4,Creports of man with weapons and
OL,5,Cstabbings
OL,7,F"Police, including firearms officers,
OL,8,Fare in attendance."
OL,10,FWilliam Ramsay, who lives in the area,
OL,11,Fsaid he believed the man with the
OL,12,Fweapons had entered the stairwell of
OL,13,Fhis building.
OL,15,F"He smashed the local shop, possibly
OL,16,Fstabbed two people unconfirmed.
OL,18,F"Armed police, dogs been here for
OL,19,Fabout two hours."
