OL,3,CEdinburgh area locked down after
OL,4,Creports of man with weapons and
OL,5,Cstabbings
OL,7,FPictures from the scene of the
OL,8,Fincident showed at least six police
OL,9,Fvehicles outside Cobbinshaw House, a
OL,10,Ftower block of flats, as well as armed
OL,11,Fpolice officers.
OL,13,FLothian Buses said its number 20
OL,14,Fservice was being diverted away from
OL,15,FCalder until further notice.
